casebody.data:
No. 3. Borrás et al. v. The District Court of Humacao. Decided April 18, 1905. *579Mr. José Guzmán Benitez, for petitioner; Messrs López Lan-drón, Eartzell and Rodríguez Berra, for opponents.

Motion to set aside an order for the issue of a writ of cer-tiorari, or otherwise, that a receiver appointed by the lower court to administer certain property in litigation be installed in office.

The motion was denied.
